FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775131865
OL,3,CMan, 36, charged with GBH after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FHe has been remanded into custody and
OL,7,Fis due to appear at Southern
OL,8,FDerbyshire Magistrates' Court on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FCounter-terrorism officers assisted
OL,12,Fthe investigation after seven people
OL,13,Fwere injured ` some seriously `
OL,14,Foutside the Bishop Blaise in Friar
OL,15,FGate at around 9.30pm on Saturday when
OL,16,Fa black Suzuki Swift mounted the
OL,17,Fpavement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1775131865
OL,3,CMan, 36, charged with GBH after
OL,4,Cpedestrians hit by car in Derby
OL,6,FThe victims were four men and three
OL,7,Fwomen aged between 36 and 52, and four
OL,8,Fhave been discharged from hospital,
OL,9,FDerbyshire Police said.
OL,11,FTheir injuries have been described by
OL,12,Fpolice as not life-threatening.
OL,14,FPonnachan, who is originally from
OL,15,FIndia but now lives in Derby, was
OL,16,Farrested seven minutes after the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
